title: Keycloak Client Libraries 26.0.4 released
content: UPGRADING  Before upgrading refer to for a complete list of changes.   ALL RESOLVED ISSUES   ENHANCEMENTS   * Wrong logger class client  * Remove JEE from the title of GH actions client  * Sync after Keycloak server 26.1.0 release client  * Test with keycloak server images 24.0, 26.0 and 26.1 client   BUGS   * ProviderTest failing with latest nightly build client  * The action "Sync with Keycloak Server and send PR with changes" sends PR,    which does not have DCO on the commit client  * The action "Sync with Keycloak Server and send PR with changes" takes only    client-common-synced into consideration client
